"title": "1065: God, holiness of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1065",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The moral excellence of God that unifies his attributes and is expressed through his actions, setting him apart from all others. Believers are called to be holy as God is holy.</p>\n<h2>God's nature is holy</h2>\n<h3>He is perfect</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:3\">ISA 6:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:8\">REV 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:31\">2SA 22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:10\">JOB 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:30\">PSA 18:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:3\">PSA 22:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:22\">PSA 71:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:41\">PSA 78:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:14\">ISA 41:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:15\">ISA 43:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:13\">HAB 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:11\">JHN 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:10\">REV 6:10</a></p>\n<h3>He is uniquely holy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:2\">1SA 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:11\">EXO 15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:13\">PSA 77:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:25\">ISA 40:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:4\">REV 15:4</a></p>\n<h2>God's name is holy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:21-Ezek36:23\">EZK 36:21–36:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:32\">LEV 22:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:35\">1CH 16:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:16\">1CH 29:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:21\">PSA 33:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:12\">PSA 97:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:25\">EZK 39:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:49\">LUK 1:49</a></p>\n<h2>God's dwelling-place is holy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a></strong> <em>David's palace was regarded as holy because of the presence of the ark</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:11\">2CH 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:27\">2CH 30:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:6\">PSA 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:4\">PSA 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:7\">PSA 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:4\">PSA 11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps15:1\">PSA 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:6\">PSA 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:8\">PSA 47:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:1\">PSA 48:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:4\">PSA 65:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:15\">ISA 63:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:17\">JOL 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:16-Obad1:17\">OBA 1:16–1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:4\">JON 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:2\">MIC 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:20\">HAB 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:13\">ZEC 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:28\">ACT 21:28</a> <em>The Jews accused Paul of defiling the temple area by bringing in Gentiles</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:21-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:21–2:22</a> <em>the church as the dwelling in which God lives by his Spirit</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:19-Heb10:22\">HEB 10:19–10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:19\">REV 22:19</a></p>\n<h2>God's holiness is revealed in his righteous activity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:16\">ISA 5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:11\">JDG 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:7\">1SA 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:13\">PSA 77:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:17\">PSA 145:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:14\">DAN 9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:16\">DAN 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:5\">ZEP 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's holiness affects worship</h2>\n<h3>It is celebrated in worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:5\">PSA 99:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:2\">PSA 29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:5\">PSA 99:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:1\">PSA 103:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:3\">PSA 105:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:21\">PSA 145:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:3\">ISA 6:3</a></p>\n<h3>Coming before a holy God requires preparation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:5\">EXO 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:37\">EXO 29:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:28\">1CO 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:1-Heb10:2\">HEB 10:1–10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a></p>\n<h3>Special requirements and tasks are given to worship leaders</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:7-Lev21:8\">LEV 21:7–21:8</a> <em>the priests</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:10-Lev21:15\">LEV 21:10–21:15</a> <em>the high priest</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:1-Exod28:43\">EXO 28:1–28:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:16-Lev21:23\">LEV 21:16–21:23</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:5\">2CH 29:5</a> <em>the Levites</em></p>\n<h2>God's holiness is to be seen in his people</h2>\n<h3>God's people are to be holy because he is holy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:2\">LEV 19:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9\">2TI 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:6\">EXO 19:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:31\">EXO 22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44\">LEV 11:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:2\">1CO 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:2\">2CO 11:2</a> <em>the church is to be pure as the bride of Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4\">EPH 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3\">EPH 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:8\">PHP 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:22\">COL 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">1TH 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:7\">1TH 4:3–4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:8\">TIT 1:8</a> <em>a qualification for an elder</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:11\">HEB 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1\">HEB 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:10\">HEB 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a></p>\n<h3>Becoming holy involves striving after God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:14\">2PE 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:22-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:22–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:22\">1TI 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:14\">HEB 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:20-Jas1:21\">JAS 1:20–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:11-2Pet3:12\">2PE 3:11–3:12</a></p>\n<h3>The holiness of believers originates from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:13\">EXO 31:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:9\">LEV 22:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:9\">DEU 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:3\">PSA 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1-1John3:3\">1JN 3:1–3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ purifies Christian believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:7\">1JN 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26-Heb7:28\">HEB 7:26–7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:26-Heb9:28\">HEB 9:26–9:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:10\">HEB 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:14\">HEB 10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:4-1John3:6\">1JN 3:4–3:6</a></p>\n<h2>God's holiness makes sin objectionable to him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:13\">HAB 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:19-Josh24:20\">JOS 24:19–24:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:29\">JER 50:29</a></p>\n<h2>God's holiness necessitates dependence upon him for forgiveness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:1-Ps51:17\">PSA 51:1–51:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4-Dan9:19\">DAN 9:4–9:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></p>",
